high_descs: Turn around, move to the counter past the sink, turn left to face the plate on the counter.
Pick up the plate on the counter.
Turn left, bring the plate to the microwave above the stove.
Heat the plate in the microwave.
Take the heated plate right to the counter, turn right, bring the plate to round dining table in the corner.
Put the plate on table near the wall, left of the book near the wall.
anns.task_desc: Put a heated plate on the dining table.

high_descs: Turn around and walk towards the counter, then turn left to face the sink.
Pick up the plate that is on the counter between the sink and the coffee machine.
Turn left and walk forward, turn right at the oven and look up at the microwave.
Open the microwave and put the plate inside, then close the microwave door and turn on the microwave, after a couple seconds open the door and remove the plate then close the door.
Turn right and walk towards the counter, then turn right and walk around the counter to the wooden table in the corner of the room.
Put the heated grey plate on the table to the left of the closest white book.
anns.task_desc: Put a heated plate on a wooden table.

high_descs: Turn around and walk across the room to the sink on your left.
Pick the plate up off of the counter next to the sink.
Turn to your left and walk across the room to the stove on your right.
Open the microwave above the stove and place the plate in the microwave. Turn the microwave on. Wait for it to turn off. Take the plate out of the microwave.
Turn to you right and walk across the room to the table in the corner on your right.
Place the plate down on the table to the left of the book.
anns.task_desc: Place a plate on the table that you picked up off of the counter and microwaved.
